headline.main: No. 20 Saint Mary's Beats Portland 81-58 in WCC Quarterfinal
headline.print_headline: No. 20 Saint Mary's Beats Portland 81-58 in WCC Quarterfinal

lead_paragraph: A stumbling Emmett Naar appeared headed for a wipeout when he suddenly regained his balance, eluded a defender and delivered a perfect behind-the-back pass to Jock Landale for an eventual three-point play.
